    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. For the lesson, I want to make sure the kids understand why this is so important. Could you expand on that last part? Specifically, can you write a paragraph that explains why focusing on the \"dignity and autonomy\" aspect is the most essential way to view substantive due process in modern law?",
